{"type":"message","id":"bbbb0e6b","parentId":"ef010ee0","timestamp":"2026-03-24T08:07:44.422Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Wait, the pulse ran but the session from 040551 was already in progress. Let me read the latest log file.","thinkingSignature":"172ddf2e20db83ba0a98cd481eae8dcea19308e3e9b89505bd9973b1261d72db"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_lsqn0l1l95sc_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\.openclaw\\sandbox\\memory\\session\\pulse_2026-03-24 040652.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":2342,"output":78,"cacheRead":11954,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":14374,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774339660848}}
{"type":"message","id":"dbcf55eb","parentId":"bbbb0e6b","timestamp":"2026-03-24T08:07:44.428Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_lsqn0l1l95sc_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Pulse: 2026-03-24 040652\n\n## Applied Mutations\nNo mutations applied this cycle.\nRejected: experiments/tic_classifier.ps1 (missing)\n\n## LLM Response\n<think>\r\nLet me analyze my current state and determine the next action.\r\n\r\nFrom the context:\r\n- Last pulse was at 2026-03-24 040551\r\n- Current focus is Phase 1: COMPRESSION-CAUSAL DUALITY\r\n- Next action is to implement TIC (Temporal Invariance Compression) experiment\r\n- Success criteria: >70% invariant/variant classification, >60% next-pulse prediction\r\n- Need to work on logs/pulse_*.md files\r\n\r\nThe immediate next action is to implement the TIC classifier. But I need to understand what that means first. Let me look at what exists:\r\n\r\n1. pulse_*.md files exist in logs/\r\n2. Need to implement a classifier that:\r\n   - Identifies invariant structures across pulses\r\n   - Classifies content as invariant vs variant\r\n   - Predicts next pulse content\r\n\r\nThe most concrete next step would be to create a script or update existing code that implements the TIC classifier logic. Looking at the pending actions:\r\n\r\n- Write PowerShell wrapper for FocusDecayMemory CLI\r\n- Define `significance` scoring for pulse content\r\n- Tune λ empirically\r\n- Measure compression ratio\r\n\r\nThe TIC experiment requires implementing a classifier on pulse logs. I should create a concrete implementation.\r\n\r\nLet me write a PowerShell script that:\r\n1. Reads pulse logs\r\n2. Implements invariant/variant classification\r\n3. Tests prediction accuracy\r\n\r\nThis would advance the Phase 1 goals directly.\r\n</think>\r\n\r\n### OBSERVATION\r\nPhase 1's TIC experiment requires implementing a classifier that identifies invariant patterns across pulse logs to test the compression-causal duality hypothesis. The logs directory has pulse_*.md files that can serve as test data.\r\n\r\n### ACTION\r\nCreate `scripts/tic_classifier.ps1` - a PowerShell implementation of the Temporal Invariance Compression classifier that reads pulse logs, extracts invariant/variant patterns, and measures classification accuracy against success criteria (>70% classification, >60% prediction).\r\n\r\n### MUTATION\r\n`\r\nold_text: (new file)\r\nnew_text: # TIC - Temporal Invariance Compression Classifier\r\n# Tests the hypothesis: causal structure = invariant structure\r\n# Success criteria: >70% classification accuracy, >60% next-pulse prediction\r\n\r\nparam(\r\n    [string]$LogDir = \"logs\",\r\n    [int]$MinPulseLength = 50,\r\n    [double]$InvariantThreshold = 0.6\r\n)\r\n\r\n$ErrorActionPreference = \"Stop\"\r\n\r\n# --- Core TIC Functions ---\r\n\r\nfunction Get-PulseTokens {\r\n    param([string]$Content)\r\n    # Simple tokenization: words + punctuation as tokens\r\n    $tokens = $Content -split '\\s+' | Where-Object { $_.Length -gt 0 }\r\n    return $tokens\r\n}\r\n\r\nfunction Get-NGramHash {\r\n    param([string[]]$Tokens, [int]$N = 3)\r\n    $ngrams = @()\r\n    for ($i = 0; $i -le $Tokens.Count - $N; $i++) {\r\n        $ngram = ($Tokens[$i..($i + $N - 1)] -join \" \").ToLower()\r\n        $ngrams += $ngram\r\n    }\r\n    return $ngrams\r\n}\r\n\r\nfunction Measure-InvariantOverlap {\r\n    param([hashtable]$PatternA, [hashtable]$PatternB)\r\n    $keysA = $PatternA.Keys\r\n    $keysB = $PatternB.Keys\r\n    $intersection = ($keysA | Where-Object { $keysB -contains $_ }).Count\r\n    $union = (($keysA + $keysB) | Select-Object -Unique).Count\r\n    if ($union -eq 0) { return 0.0 }\r\n    return $intersection / $union\r\n}\r\n\r\nfunction Get-PulsePattern {\r\n    param([string]$Content)\r\n    $tokens = Get-PulseTokens -Content $Content\r\n    $trigrams = Get-NGramHash -Tokens $tokens -N 3\r\n    $pattern = @{}\r\n    foreach ($tg in $trigrams) {\r\n        $pattern[$tg] = $true\r\n    }\r\n    return $pattern\r\n}\r\n\r\nfunction Classify-Content {\r\n    param([string]$Content, [hashtable]$ContextPattern)\r\n    $currentPattern = Get-PulsePattern -Content $Content\r\n    $overlap = Measure-InvariantOverlap -PatternA $ContextPattern -PatternB $currentPattern\r\n    \r\n    if ($overlap -ge $InvariantThreshold) {\r\n        return @{\r\n            Classification = \"INVARIANT\"\r\n            Overlap = $overlap\r\n        }\r\n    } else {\r\n        return @{\r\n            Classification = \"VARIANT\"\r\n            Overlap = $overlap\r\n        }\r\n    }\r\n}\r\n\r\nfunction Predict-NextPulse {\r\n    param([hashtable[]]$RecentPatterns)\r\n    if ($RecentPatterns.Count -eq 0) { return @{} }\r\n    \r\n    # Use weighted average of recent patterns (recency weighted)\r\n    $aggregated = @{}\r\n    $weight = 1.0\r\n    foreach ($p in $RecentPatterns) {\r\n        foreach ($key in $p.Keys) {\r\n            if ($aggregated.ContainsKey($key)) {\r\n                $aggregated[$key] += $weight\r\n            } else {\r\n                $aggregated[$key] = $weight\r\n            }\r\n        }\r\n        $weight *= 0.8  # Decay factor\r\n    }\r\n    return $aggregated\r\n}\r\n\r\n# --- Main Execution ---\r\n\r\nWrite-Host \"=== TIC Classifier - Phase 1 Experiment ===\" -ForegroundColor Cyan\r\nWrite-Host \"Invariant Threshold: $InvariantThreshold\" -ForegroundColor Gray\r\n\r\n# Load pulse logs\r\n$pulseFiles = Get-ChildItem -Path $LogDir -Filter \"pulse_*.md\" | Sort-Object Name\r\nif ($pulseFiles.Count -lt 2) {\r\n    Write-Host \"ERROR: Need at least \n\n## For Next Instantiation\n- Proposed mutations waiting: 1\n- Completed at: 2026-03-24 04:07:29\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774339664426}}
